main event: Crew of missile support objects observed 3 reddish lights in the sky over Haviland, Kansas.
interesting points: The objects were described as having no exhaust and making no sound., They appeared to move irregularly and danced as they moved., The observation lasted for approximately 30 minutes., The objects were described as half-moon shaped with a bright light on the east edge., The report concluded the sightings were insufficient for further evaluation.
sighted object: three reddish lights in the sky
